## Full Stack Architecture

### Frontend (Client)
- **Framework**: [React](https://react.dev/) with [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/) for fast development.
- **Styling**: [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/) and [Framer Motion](https://www.framer.com/motion/) for premium, fluid animations.
- **UI Components**: [Radix UI](https://www.radix-ui.com/) and [Lucide](https://lucide.dev/) icons for accessible, modern design.
- **State Management**: [TanStack Query](https://tanstack.com/query/latest) for robust server state management.

### Backend (Server)
- **Runtime**: [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) with [Express](https://expressjs.com/).
- **Database**: [SQLite](https://www.sqlite.org/) with [Drizzle ORM](https://orm.drizzle.team/) for type-safe database access.
- **Authentication**: [Passport.js](https://www.passportjs.org/) for secure session-based authentication.
- **AI Integration**: Custom OCR engine for glucose report analysis using OpenAI.

### Shared (Type-Safe Schema)
- Unified schema and API route definitions using [Zod](https://zod.dev/) to ensure 100% type safety between the frontend and backend.

